OPCIÓN 1: Netlify (Recomendado)
  1. https://app.netlify.com
  2. Import from Git
  3. Build: npm run build
  4. Publish: dist
  5. Env vars:
     VITE_SUPABASE_URL
     VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY

OPCIÓN 2: Vercel
  1. https://vercel.com
  2. Import project
  3. Auto-detecta Vite
  4. Same env vars

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
